title: Volodymyr Kornutyak
text: Volodymyr Kornutyak (; born 24 July 1983 in <a href="Ukrainian%20SSR">Ukrainian SSR</a>) is a <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">defender</a> who plays for <a href="FC%20Mynai">FC Mynai</a> in the <a href="Ukrainian%20Second%20League">Ukrainian Second League</a>.
